{
  "page": "Little Valyrian",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:LittleValyrian_by_Kevin_Catalan.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b1/LittleValyrian_by_Kevin_Catalan.jpg/350px-LittleValyrian_by_Kevin_Catalan.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"246\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b1/LittleValyrian_by_Kevin_Catalan.jpg/525px-LittleValyrian_by_Kevin_Catalan.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b1/LittleValyrian_by_Kevin_Catalan.jpg/700px-LittleValyrian_by_Kevin_Catalan.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:LittleValyrian_by_Kevin_Catalan.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A Little Valyrian, by Kevin Catalan ©</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>Little Valyrian</b> is a species of <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lemur\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Lemur\">lemur</a> that lives in the <a href=\"/index.php/Forest_of_Qohor\" title=\"Forest of Qohor\">Forest of Qohor</a>. They have silver-white fur and huge <a href=\"/index.php/Purple_eyes\" title=\"Purple eyes\">purple eyes</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf823_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf823-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#About\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">About</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"About\">About</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Little_Valyrian&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: About\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Little_Valyrians_by_AljunaibiiM.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ea/Little_Valyrians_by_AljunaibiiM.jpg/300px-Little_Valyrians_by_AljunaibiiM.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"381\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ea/Little_Valyrians_by_AljunaibiiM.jpg/450px-Little_Valyrians_by_AljunaibiiM.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ea/Little_Valyrians_by_AljunaibiiM.jpg/600px-Little_Valyrians_by_AljunaibiiM.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Little_Valyrians_by_AljunaibiiM.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Little Valyrians, by AljunaibiiM ©</div></div></div>\n<p>Although most lemurs in the <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a> live in the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Sothoryos\" title=\"Sothoryos\">Sothoryos</a>, there is one species that can be found much farther north, in the <a href=\"/index.php/Forest_of_Qohor\" title=\"Forest of Qohor\">Forest</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Qohor\" title=\"Qohor\">Qohor</a>. These lemurs have silver-white fur and huge purple eyes, and are called Little Valyrians because they share the famous <a href=\"/index.php/Valyria\" title=\"Valyria\">Valyrian</a> racial traits.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf823_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf823-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>A preserved example of one of these lemurs can be found stuffed and mounted in the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a>. So many hands of would-be <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">maesters</a> have patted it for luck in their examinations, its fur has long since fallen out.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf823_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf823-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Little_Valyrian&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Little_Valyrian&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> travels with Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a>'s <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khalasar\" title=\"Khalasar\">khalasar</a></i> through the <a href=\"/index.php/Forest_of_Qohor\" title=\"Forest of Qohor\">Forest of Qohor</a> for half a month. Dany is aware that lemurs with silver fur and huge purple eyes live in the forest, but all the animals flee before the approach of the <i>khalasar</i> and she gets no glimpse of them.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Little_Valyrian&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_23\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 23\">Chapter 23</a>, Daenerys III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf823-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf823_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf823_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf823_2-2\">2.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Sunset Kingdom&#58; The Free Cities&#32;(Qohor).</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100